\id JAS - Ndwewe Bible Version
\h Yakobo
\toc1 Lihamba kuhuma kwa YAKOBU
\toc2 Yakobo
\toc3 Yak
\mt2 Lihamba kuhuma kwa
\mt1 YAKOBU
\imt1 Ulongolelo
\ip Kitabho aki kya Yakobo kikityekwa na mundu yumu ywakakemitwe Yakobo. Yinguhyubhalika kukita pangi Yakobo ayu kakibhegha nnongo ghwake Yesu, ywakabheghite kilongohi mu ngwemuko lya bhandu bhaanhyubhalilite kilisito bha makachu, na kakibhegha mjumbe ywa hilongohi ghwa njenga kaya, mukitabho kya Andumilwa, kipalamande kya 15:13. Nndumilwa Paulo bhubho kakinkema Yakobo “Ngimiko” ya ngwemuko lya bhandu bha anhyubhalilite kilisito, mukitabho kya Akaagalatia, kipalamande kya 2:9. Asomi bhanguhyubhalila kukita kitabho kya Yakobo kikityekwa yikali ya ngungwa ya mbindamabhoko nhano mbole ya kubhelekwa Kilisito. Kiyaha Yakobo kakibhegha kilongohi ghwa ngwemuko ya bhandu bha anhyubhalilite Kilisito akwo Yelusalemu, yinguhyubhalika kukita kakilyeka lihamba ali pakabheghite kangutama ku Yelusalemu.
\ip Yakobo kakilityeka kitabho aki kwa “Makabila mbinda mabhoko yimo na abhili yiipwilinganikite mu milima” 1:1. Mahundo ghaabheghite mu kitabu kya Yakobo, ghanguanogha ahyubhalila bhoha, peni lilagho “Kabila mbinda mabhoko yimo na abhili” ghangutenda tumanye kukita pangi Yakobo kakiatyekelagha Akaayahudi bhaanhyubhalilite Kilisto. Kiyaha kitabho aki kikialinga kuahikila asomi atangalo. Yakobo kakilinga malingano mu kuhyubhalila na mandendelo. Kuhyubhalila kwa hoto kuubhoneha mu mandendelo, kipalamande kya 2:17. Kangi kakiakinya bhando kwa kulema kwa kubhonela ubhaghulo kwa bhaabheghite na utopelo, kipalamande kya 2:1-4 na kakitulongela yakya kulindakila kwa ghala ghatughalongela, kipalamande kya 3:1-12.
\iot Ghaabheghite
\io1 Yakobo kanguajambua asomaji bhake mu 1:1.
\io1 Mbole kanguayonjokeha mwoyo bhandu bhaanhyubhalila Kilsto 1:2-27
\io1 Kangi kangulubhulila yakya bhula payikwiliha kuhyubhalila kubhonehwa kwa mandendelo 2:1-26
\io1 Mbole kangulubhulila yakya bhula malagho paghabhegha na makakala 3:1-12
\io1 Kangi kangulubhulila bhula mahala gha Chapanga paghabhegha kihyengo na mahala gha anabhandu 3:13—4:10
\io1 Mbole kanguakinya hilongohi bhake yakya mihalo ya kulikweha, kipalamande kya 4:11—5:6
\io1 Yakobo kanguyomolela kitabho kyake kwa kuapegha malaghilo gha kighughumu, kipalamande kya 5:7-20
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nenga Yakobo, mmandwa ghwa Chapanga na ghwa Bambo Yesu Kilisito.
\p Nunguatyekela makabila kumi na mabhili gha Akaayahudi ghaapwilinganite munnima. Mwika.
\s1 Kuhyubhalila na malango
\p 
\v 2 Maalongo bhangu mapungwo nhanganganiko paghabhahikila, mwenga mughabhone ndo handa kihokonyo kya kubhegha na kindimba kikulu.
\v 3 Kiyaha mungumanya kukita kuyighwa kwa uhyubhalilo ghwenu kunguayeghela mwenga nnyonjokeheke kulimbililo.
\v 4 Basi nng'endelel kulimbilil mbaka kuuhiko, ngati mmokole kubhegha atwihiliko yomo.
\v 5 Peni handa yumu ywenu pakapelelwa na malango uhyubhalilo ndo yingunkwiliha kunnyupa kwa Chapanga, naywo Chapanga katanpegha kwa utekulo, katakalala ng'obhe, ngati kataapegha bhoha kwa utangalo.
\v 6 Peni kayupe kwa kuhyubhalaila kyanga lyogha lyohele kukita kaamokola ebhu kaamokaola ng'obhe. Mundu ywakabhegha na lyogha ndo handa lidaba lya lihibha linakutakulwa kwa liyegha kuno na akwo.
\v 7 Kiyaha mundu handa ayo kakotoke kuhwacha kukita katakingama kyohele kuhuma kwa Bambo.
\v 8 Mundu ghwa mahwacho mabhili katanyumanyuma mu njila hyake hyoha.
\s1 Ukapukwa na utopelo
\p 
\v 9 Peni kapukwa ywakanhyubhalila Kilisito kangunoghwa kayelelwe, kiyaha Chapanga kangummona ywombe ndo ywa maha,
\v 10 naywo yunautopelo kangunoghwa kayelelwe pala Chapanga pakaatenda abheghe bhanakuhwama. Kiyaha bhombe bhanguhwegha handa malubha gha kumanyahi.
\v 11 Nkenga paghu homoka na mbwipila yake ngalipa yingunyaluha manyahi, nagho malubha ghake ghaanyaluka na umaha ghwake ghungukanjanganika. Ubhwabhu abhu, yunautopelo katakanjaghanwa mumakakaliko ghake.
\s1 Chapanga kangunng'eha ng'obhe mundu
\p 
\v 12 Kanonelwa mundu ywakahighala nhyubhaliko mu mang'eho, handa pakahotola kulimbilila, katapeghwa lilumbo lya ubhumi lyene Chapanga kakialagha bhala bhaampala.
\v 13 Mundu pakang'ehwa kakotoke kulongela, “Nungung'ehwa na Chapanga.” Kiyaha Chapanga kahone kuyighwa kwa uhakata, na mwene kahone kunnyigha mundu ywohele.
\v 14 Peni mundu kangung'ehwa na kukuluhwa na kughomelwa tama hyake pakahutwa.
\v 15 Pala tama ahyo pahikamala hinguntenda mundu katende ulemwa na ulemwa paghukamala ghunguyegha kiho.
\p 
\v 16 Maalongo bhangu bhanuapala, nkotoke kukuluhwa!
\v 17 Kyohele kiibhuhwa na kiibhegha kya maha na kinakutwihilika ndo kunguhuma kwa Tate mmumba ghwa mibhwelo yoha ya kunani. Ywombe kingughilimbuka ng'obhe, ebu kabheghang'obhe na mango yohele ya kughalambuka.
\v 18 Kwa mapalo ghake mwene kakitupapa kwa lilagho lyake lya hoto, ili tubheghe handa malimbulo gha ulongohi.
\s1 Kuyihwa na kutenda
\p 
\v 19 Maalongo bhangu bhanuapala, nkulungwe nnando aghu! Mundu ywohele kayumbatike kuyihwa peni chepa kayumbatike mukulongela ebu mukukalala.
\v 20 Kiyaha mundu ywakabhegha na kiyaghabhu kanguhotola ng'obhe ktutegnda ghakaghapala Chapanga.
\v 21 Kya habhu, nnekane na matamilo gha uhakata ghwoha na mandendelo mahakataho, mulibhike pahi ya utabhala ghwa Chapanga na kuyitikila lilagho liipanditwe mu myoyo yenu, alyo ndo lyahotola kubhalopoha.
\p 
\v 22 Nkotoke kukuluhana mabhene kwa kuyihwa lilagho lya Chapanga ghweka, ngati ntende handa lilagho mulilongela.
\v 23 Kiyaha mundu pakabhegha kanguyihwa lilagho ghweka kyanga kulitenda, mundu aywo ndo handa mundu yunakulilolekeha mu lindala,
\v 24 kangulibhona mwene na pakabhuka mu lindala, kamu kangulibhalila bhula pakabhegha.
\v 25 Peni mundu ywakalolekeha muno malaghilo matwihiliko ghaabhapegha bhandu uhulu, mundu ywakaghendelela kughahungila, na kakotoke kuyihwa ghweka na mbole kughalibhalila, maha ndo kangutenda handa paghapala agho malaghilo, mundu aywo ndo katanonelwa mu kila kilibhi kyaapala kukitenda.
\v 26 Handa mundu katalibhona kanguntughila Chapanga kwa njila yinakunoghwa peni kangulikanila ng'obhe kutabhala lulimi lwake, kuntundamila Chapanga kwa ywombe, chepa kilibhi na kangulikuluha mwene.
\v 27 Mundu ywakantundamila Chapanga muyiunoghwa Kutundamila kwa maha na kwanga kinyakali muulongolo ghwa Tate Chapanga ndo aku, Kubhatangatila bhana alekwa na adala alekwa mu ghala ghaaghapala, na kulingikiha na matamilo gha bhandu bhanga kunhyubhalila Chapanga.
\c 2
\s1 Nneke kuabhaghula bhandu Lukinyo kwakya ubhaghulo
\p 
\v 1 Maalongo bhangu, kiyaha munhyubhalila Bambo ghwetu Yesu Kilisito, Bambo ghwa ukulu, nkotoke kubhabhaghula bhandu,
\v 2 kwa nhwano, kayingila mundu mu nyumba ya kuntundamila Chapanga, kahwala pete ya sahabu na mapinda gha maha, mbole kayingila kapukwa ywakahwalite lipinda litukutuku,
\v 3 na mwenga mungunhwamila yula ywakahwalite mapinda gha maha na kunng'ombela, “Ghutame apa pamaha.” Na kunyuyuha kapukwa, “Ghwenga ghuyime pala, ebu ghutame pahi ugheghela na nenga.”
\v 4 Bhuli! Aghwo chepa ubhaghulo mu mwenga? Bhuli aghwo ulamulo ghwenu ghungubhukana ng'obhe na mahwacho mahakata?
\p 
\v 5 Maalongo bhangu nnyihwe, Chapanga kabhahaghula bhandu bhaabheghite kapukwa munnima aghu ili abheghe atopelo mu kunhyubhalila Kilisto na kukingama kwa bhala bhaampala.
\v 6 Peni mwenga mungu ayuyuha makapukwa, bhuli? Abho atopelo bhanguabhonela ng'obhe na kubhatola kughenda mumabalasa?
\v 7 Bhuli, ndo abho ng'obhe bhaaliligha lihina lya maha lya Bambo ghwetu?
\p 
\v 8 Peni handa pamulitwihiliha lila lilaghilo lya kibhutwa handa palityekitwe mu malembo gha Chapanga, “Ghunpale nndamani ghwako handa paghulipala ghumene” Ndo maabhegha mungutenda gha maha.
\v 9 Peni pamubhabhaghula bhandu mungutenda ulemwa, nagho malaghilo ghanguatosa mwenga kukita nhokela.
\v 10 Ywakadunyula ngwiliho yimu mu malaghilo, katabhegha nhokelo ghwa kughadunyula malaghilo ghoha.
\v 11 Kiyaha yuyula Chapang ywakalongilite, “Ghukotokye kubhegha ntyahe” kakilongela bhubho, “Ghukotoke kukoma.” Kya habho, payibhele ghukityaha ng'obhe, peni ghukoma, ghwenga ghughadunyula malaghilo.
\v 12 Hino, nnongele na kutenda handa bhandu bhaapala kutoswa na malaghilo ghanakuyegha uhulu.
\v 13 Kiyaha Chapanga katabhegha ng'obhe na luhungu pakantosa mundu ywakabhegha ng'obhe na luhungu. Peni luhungu lunguhotola toso.
\s1 Kuhyubhalila na kutenda pakapala Chapanga
\p 
\v 14 Maalongo bhangu, yingutangatila niki mundu pakalongela kukita kanauhyubhalilo, peni kangubhoneha ng'obhe mandendelo? Bhuli, kuhyubhalila akwo kwahotola kunnopola?
\v 15 Kwa nhwano, nnongo ebu nhacha kabhegha na mapinda matukutuku ebu ywanga hilyo.
\v 16 Na yumoo ywenu pakaaghombela, “Nngende kwa uhihimilo makayote mwoto na makayukute,” kyanga kubhapegha ghala ghaaghapala mu kutama kwabhe?
\v 17 Ubhwabhu abhu yingutangatila niki, uhyubhalilo ghweka kyanga mandendelo ndo uhyubhalila akwo kuhwegha.
\p 
\v 18 Peni mundu kaalongela, “Ghwenga ghubhegha na uhyubhalilo, na nenga mmegha na mandendelo!” Maha, peni ghunmonehe mundu pakahotola kubhegha na uhyubhalilo kyanga mandendelo, na nenga ndakubhoneha uhyubhalilo ghwangu kwa mandendelo ghangu.
\v 19 Ghwenga ghunguhyubhalila kukita Chapanga ndo yumo, ghungutenda maha. Mandilu nabho bhanguhyubhalila na kuloghoya kwa lyogha.
\v 20 Nghwenga ndo nbhughabhugha! Ghungubhona ng'obhe kukita uhyubhalilo kyanga mandendelo ghuhwegha?
\v 21 Bhuli, tate ghwetu Ibulahimu kakimokola bhuli kuyitikilwa kukita ghwa maha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga? Kwa mandendelo ghake, pala pakanbhuhite mwana ghwake Isaka kubhegha nyambi mu likuta.
\v 22 Hinu ghungubhona kukita kuhyubhalila kwake kukibhegha papamu na mandendelo ghake, kuhyubhalila kwake kukitwihilika kubhukana na mandendelo ghake.
\v 23 Habho ghakitwihilika ghala malembo gha Chapanga ghaalongelilte, “Ibulahimu kakinhyubhalila Chapanga na kwa kuhyubhalila kwake kakiyitikilwa kukita ndo mundu ywa maha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga,” na habho Ibulahimu kakikemwa ghanja ghwa Chapanga.
\v 24 Mungubhona kukita mungu kaayitikilwa kukita ghwa maha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga kwa mandendelo ghake, na kata kwa kuhyubhalila ghweka.
\p 
\v 25 Rahabu ywakabheghite ntyahe ndo nhwano ghungi, ywombe kakibhonekana ghwa maha muulongolo ghwa Chapanga kwa mandendelo ghake, pala pakaahihite bhala ahingukiha kitami na kubhatangatila abhuke kwa kupitila njila yingi.
\p 
\v 26 Hinu, handa bhula mmili kyanga nhuki ghuhwegha, ubhwabhu abhu kuhyubhalila kyanga mandendelo ndo kuhwegha.
\c 3
\s1 Lulimi
\p 
\v 1 Maalongo bhangu, nkotoke kubhegha ahunda atangalo mu mwenga kiyaha mamanya kukita maamokola toso ngulu.
\v 2 Kiyaha twabhoha tunguhokela mu milando mitangalo. Mundu ywangahokela mu kulongela aywo ndo mundu ntwihiliko, kanguhotola kughukanikiha mmili ghwake ghoha handa kwa lijamu.
\v 3 Twenga ngubhika lijamu munnomo ghwa Falasi ngati bhatuyitikile, na kwa njila ayo tunguhotolakubhalongoha kwohele kutukupala.
\v 4 Ubhabhu abhu meli, payibhele ndo ngulu muno, na yingugheghwa na liyegha likalipa, peni yingukibhuhwa na sukani nndokwa muno, na yingughenda pwohele pakapala nnyendeha.
\v 5 Ubhwabhu abhu, payibhele lulimi ndo kibhungo kidokwa muno mu mmili, peni lungulitikila milando mikulu muno.
\p Mwoto nnokwa ghwahotola kukanjaghana nsitu nkulu.
\v 6 Ubhwabhu abhu, lulimi ndo handa mwoto. Ghumema uhakata ntangalo, ghubhegha na ng'ebhu yake mumimili yetu na ghungughukwila uhakata mumitima yetu yoha. Lungukanjaghana ubhumi ghwetu ghoha kwa mwoto ghuuhuma kumambe.
\v 7 Mundu kanguhotola kuhuha anyama na kahotola kuhuha anyama bhoha, anyama bha kunhitu, hiyuni na miyoka na hibhumbe ya mulihibha.
\v 8 Peni kahone mundu ywakahotola kuluhuha lulimi, lulimi ndo kilibhi kihakata, kabhone kulutabhala, na lumema lusungu lunakukoma.
\v 9 Kwa lulimi twenga tungunnumba Bambo na Tate ghwetu, kwa lulimi alwo tunguakundula bhandu, bhandu bhaabhumbitwe kwa nhwano ghwa Chapanga.
\v 10 Malagho gha kunemela na kukundula ghoha ghanguhuma mu nnomo ghumo. Maalongo bhangu milando aywo yingunogha ng'obhe kubhegha handa habho.
\v 11 Bhuli, chemchem yimo yahotola kubhuha machi gha maha na mahakata papamo?
\v 12 Maalongo bhangu, bhuli, nkongo ghwa tini ghwaahotola kupambika tini? Chemchem ya machi gha mwinyu yahotola ngobhe kubhuha machi gha maha.
\s1 Malango kuhuma kunani
\p 
\v 13 Ndo ghani ywakabhegha na mahala na malango mu mwenga? Kangi kabhonehe nnando aghwo kwa matamilo gha maha, ghanakutendeka kwa kuhwama na malango.
\v 14 Hinu handa myoyo yenu yimema tama hakataho, kukalala na ghwimi, basi, nkotoke kulitika na kulongela uhwangi kihyengo kya hoto.
\v 15 Malango handa agho ghanguhuma ng'obhe kunani, malango agho ndo ghamunnima kangi ndo gha nchipila.
\v 16 Kiyaha pohele paabhegha na tama hakataho na ghwimi, apo pabhegha na bhulwa na uhakata nhanganganiko.
\v 17 Peni malango ghanakuhuma kunani kwa Chapanga, kangi ghangututenda tubheghe bha nyani muulongolo ghwa Chapanga, ghangupala uhihimilo, utokomaho na ghanguapala bhandu, ghamema lipyanda na ghabhegha na ghangutangatila kutenda gha maha, ghakahone ubhaghulo ebu ufyangu.
\v 18 Bhandu bhanakuyegha uhihimilo nkati ya bhandu bhangubhegha handa bhangupanda mbeyu ya uhihimilo. Mbole bhatabhena ghanakunoghwa muulongolo ghwa Chapanga.
\c 4
\s1 Ughanja na nnima
\p 
\v 1 Mikoha yinguhuma kwoki, na matutano nkati yenu ghanguhuma kwoki? Ghanguhuma mu tama yenu hakata yiitutana ngondo mu nkati yenu?
\v 2 Mungupala kubhegha na hilibhi na kiyaha munguhimokola ng'obhe ndo mungukoma bhandu, mungupala muno kubhegha na hilibhi, peni kuhimokola ng'obhe, habhu mungulimbana na kututana. Mungumokola ng'obhe hila himuhipala kiyaha mungunnyupa ng'obhe Chapanga.
\v 3 Kangi pannyupa munguhimokola ng'obhe kiyaha munguyupa kwa ningo hakataho, ili mmokole kuhitumila ahyo hinpala kumokola kwa tama hyenu hakataho.
\v 4 Mwenga mangahyubhalika handa atyahe, Bhuli mungumanya ng'obhe kukita kupalwa na nnima ndo umyanja na Chapanga? Kya habhu, ywohele ywakapala kubhegha nng'anja ghwa nnima kangutendeka nmyanja ghwa Chapanga.
\v 5 Nkotoke kuhwacha kukita malembo gha Chapanga ghangulongela malagho gha yaghi, paghalongela, “Aghwo Nhuki, ywakabhikitwe na Chapanga nkati yetu kabhegha na malili makulu”
\v 6 Peni ywombe kangutupegha twenga umaha kyanalumu. Habhu ndo mana malembo gha Chapanga ghangulongela, “Chapanga kanguapingika bhaabheghite na ngangatala peni kanguapegha nonelo bhanakuhwama.”
\p 
\v 7 Hinu munnyitikile Chapanga. Munpingikihe Nchipila naywo kataatugha.
\v 8 Munheghelele Chapanga, naywo kataaheghelela mwenga. Mwenga mummeghite na ulemwa mughuleke ulemwa ghwenu ntende gha maha! Na muyitendekehe myoyo yenu yibheghe ya nyani mwenga mummeghite na ningo mbili!
\v 9 Myoyo yinu yibhabhine, nlile na kukulika, kuheka kwa mwenga na kubheghe kililo, na kuyeylela kwa mwenga kubheghe ngukuliko ngulu.
\v 10 Nhwame muulongolo ghwa Chapanga, naywo kataayinula.
\s1 Lukinyo kwakya kuatosa bhangi
\p 
\v 11 Maalongo, nkotoke kughomelana mahakata mabhene, ywakanng'ombela uhakata nnongo ghwake na kuntosa, kangulongela uhakata kwakya malaghilo na kulongela malaghilo ghangunoghwa ng'obhe. Paghulongela malaghilo ghangunoghwa ng'obhe, ghwenga ghungughayitikila ng'obhe ngati ghungughalema.
\v 12 Chapanga ghweka chake ndo ywakaghabhikite malaghilo na toso. Ywombe ghweka chake ndo ywakahotola kulopoha na kukanjaghana. Hinu ghwenga ndo ghani mbaka ghunguntasa mundu nnyako?
\s1 Lukinyo kwakya kulikweha
\p 
\v 13 Basi, mwenga nnyihwe na munakulongela, “Lelo ebu kilabho twaaghenda mu kitami kimu na kutama akwo ngungwa yoha twaachuusa na kumokola ngalabha ngenju.”
\v 14 Mwenga mungumanja ng'obhe hata kiipala kubwituka kilabho! Mwenga ndo handa unguungweta ghuubwituka kya mandina na kubhuka.
\v 15 Yinguanogha kulongela, “Handa pakapala Chapanga, twaatama na kutenda aki na kila”
\v 16 Peni hinu mungulitika na kulighamba, kulighamba kwakya luhumu alu ndo uhakata.
\p 
\v 17 Basi mundu ywakamanya kughatenda gha maha, peni kangutenda ng'obhe ghama, mundu aywo kangutenda ulemwa.
\c 5
\s1 Lukinyo kwa bhandu bha abheghite na Utopelo
\p 
\v 1 Hinu, nnyihwe mwenga maatopelo! Nlile na kutunila kwa kya mapughwo ghaapala kubhahikila.
\v 2 Utopelo ghwenu ghubhola, na maghwanda ghenu ghalighwa na hipuluputu.
\v 3 Sahabu hyenu na madini ghanakukemwa fesa hyabukutulwa na kutu, na kutu yake yaabhabhoneha na kubukutula mibhili yenu handa bhula mwoto. Kiyaha mwenga mulibhikila utopelo mu manjubha agha gha uhiko.
\v 4 Mukiapegha ng'obhe mbiya bhala bhaatenda mahengo mu mighunda yenu. Hinu, nnyihwe kililo kyabhe pabhakukulika abho bhaabena mu mighunda yenu, kihika mu makutu gha Bambo yuna mchonda.
\v 5 Mwenga ntama na kuliyeleha kwa kutenda utyahe mu nnma aghu. Nlyegha na kubhegha maha handa nnyama ywakabhikitwe kala kwakya linjubha lya kuhinjwa.
\v 6 Mubhatosa na kubhakoma bhandu bhanga kutenda uhokelo, bhandu bhanga kupingikana na mwenga.
\s1 Ulimbililo na kuyupa
\p 
\v 7 Maalongo bhangu, ng'endelele kulimbilila kunu pannindila mbaka pakabhuya Bambo Yesu Kilisto. Nkulungwe bhula nkulima pakalimbilila na kulindila mimela yake yipambike mabeno gha ngalabha. Ywombe kangulindila kwa kulimbilila hula ya ntulo na kihuku.
\v 8 Ubhwabhu abhu na mwenga mungunoghwa kubhegha na ulimbililo, kangi mulibhike kala, kiyaha kuhika kwa Bambo kubhegha ugheghela.
\p 
\v 9 Maalongo, nkotoke kubhayilana ili nkotoke kutoswa na Chapanga. Nnole nnamula kabhegha kala kuyingila mu njengakaya.
\v 10 Maalongo, handa mungupala kughubhona nhwano ghwa kulimbilila mu mapughwo, mubhakulungwe ambuye bhaalondolite handa Bambo pakaaghombelite bhalongele.
\v 11 Tungubhakema bhombe anonelwa kiyaha bhakilimbilila. Nyihwa nhalo ghwa kulimbilila kwa Ayubu, na mungumanya bhula Chapanga pakantendilite kuuhiko. Kiyaha Chapanga ndo yuna luhungu na lipyanda.
\p 
\v 12 Kupitingana kwa agho ghoha, maalongo, nkotoke kulapa kwa kunane, ebu kwa nnima aghu, ebu kwa kilibhi kingi kyohele. Nnongele “Ena” handa mana yenu ndo ena, na “Kabhone” handa mana yenu ndo kahone, na apwo maatoswa ng'obhe na Chapanga.
\p 
\v 13 Bhuli, mundu ywohele mu mwenga kabhegha mu mapughwo? Hinu, kangunoghwa kayupe. Bhuli, kabhegha ywohele kanguyelelwa? Hino, kayimbe miyimbo ya kutika.
\v 14 Bhuli, kabhegha ywohele mu mwenga kangulwalwa? Aywo kangunoghwa kuabhakema hilongohi bha ngwemuko, nabho bhatanyupila na kuntyeka mahuta kwa lihina lya Bambo Yesu Kilisito.
\v 15 Abho hilongohi, paayupa kwa kuhyubhalila, kula kuyupa kwa kuhyubhalila kutantenda mundu aywo kalamihwe, Bambo katampegha upughwo, na ulemwa ghwakatendite ghwaalekekehwa.
\v 16 Hinu, nlekekehane ulemwa ghwenu, na nnyupilane, ili mmokole kulamihwa. Mayupo gha mundu ywakatenda gha kunnogheha Chapanga ghabhegha na makakala gha kutenda milando mitangalo.
\v 17 Eliya kakibhegha mundu handa twenga. Kakiyupa kwa ubhinililo kukita hula yikotoke kukoma, na hula yikikoma ng'obhe munnima kwa ngungwa ndatu na nusu.
\v 18 Mbole, kakiyupa kangi na hula yikikoma na nnima ghkibhuha mapambika ghake.
\p 
\v 19 Maalongo bhangu, yumu mu mwenga pakahokela na kuyileka hoto, naywo pakabhuyihwa na mundu yungi,
\v 20 mmanye kukita ywombe ywakanbhuyihite yuna ulemwa, kuhuma ku uhokelo ghwake, katalopoleghwa nhuki ghwake kuhuma mu kiho na katalekekehwa ulemwa ghwake ghwoha.
